# Local biometric capture data + diagnostic tools (untracked but sensitive
# on the now-public repo; explicit gitignore prevents accidental `git add .`
# exposure of real player capture data — exactly the data the protocol's
# whole architecture protects from leaving the local machine).
.gic_monitor.py
.phase235_biometric_collector.py
.phase235_biometric_data_*.jsonl
.phase235_biometric_summary_*.json

